headline: Procare Solutions Releases 2025 Child Care Business Trends Report
summary: Procare Solutions, a leader in child care management software for more than 30 years, released our third annual report on early childhood education and the child care industry. For the first time, the data-packed report includes a teacher-focused supplement, including what challenges they face and how directors can support them.
